briefdescription.para: YouCompleteMe configuration that interprets a .clang_complete file.

detaileddescription.para: This module implementes the YouCompleteMe configuration API documented at: https://github.com/ycm-core/ycmd#ycm_extra_confpy-specification
The implementation loads and processes a .clang_complete file, documented at: https://github.com/xavierd/clang_complete/blob/master/README.md
